TV and radio presenter Lerato Kganyago has finally tied the knot. The media personality first confirmed her marriage to businessman Thami Ndlala earlier this week on Metro FM when she said: “I'm a married woman.” Yesterday, Lerato finally celebrated her traditional wedding and celebrities attended, notably Metro FM's Dineo Ranaka and Naked DJ, as well as Idols SA judge Somizi Mhlongo. SEE PICS AND VIDEOS: My Family over everything ?? A post shared by  Leratokganyago?? (@leratokganyago) on Mar 21, 2020 at 11:25am PDT 